OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry and
OL,6,Fsunny into the evening, with clear
OL,7,Fspells overnight, cloud increasing
OL,8,Ffrom the west towards dawn. Much
OL,9,Fcooler than recent nights. Mostly
OL,10,Flight southwesterly winds, but always
OL,11,Fa little breezier near coasts and in
OL,12,Fthe north..
OL,13,
OL,14,CMonday:FRather cloudy with some bright
OL,15,For sunny spells across especially into
OL,16,Fthe afternoon. Temperatures close to
OL,17,Fthe late June average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
